{
  "texts": [
    "The network's feature extraction capability is enhanced, and the influence of noise is successfully decreased.",
    "Figure 3 depicts its structural diagram.",
    "The AMC2fLEFEM module combines the learned features with the C2f convolution branch to gain more gradient features and semantic information.",
    "This module combines the SimAM attention mechanism with the extraction of low-level features.",
    "It is worth noting that this is not merely using an attention mechanism."
  ]
}